        <p>
            A kill fee is exactly what it sounds like – if customer has cancelled the order in between of the work assigned to Freelancer for whatever reason (Customer goes bankrupt, cancels the project, not satisfied with the quality you are serving, change of mind, etc.),
            then Express Video will pay a 50% of the agreed price of their Freelancer fees for the partial work they have done.
        </p>
    </section>

