        </p>
        <p>a)	10% deduction from their freelancer fees, if there is a delay of 1 day in delivery </p>
        <p>b)	25% deduction from their freelancer fees, if there is a delay of 2 days in delivery</p>
        <p>c)	50% deduction from their freelancer fees, if there is a delay of 3 days in delivery</p>
        <p>Due to any reason, if the freelancer surrenders or cancel the “Work Order” accepted by him, they will have to immediately call us and inform us on our customer care number.</p>
    </section>

